{"tid":2187392,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"為什麼很多留學生都說香港不悶, 外國很悶?","createTime":"2020-09-03T14:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T16:19:36.000Z","uid":272077,"like":6,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"81883ce2f8ab3d5fc744b9ebce1fbaa1354631e0","tid":2187392,"uid":272077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T14:58:28.000Z","msg":"為什麼很多人都說香港不悶, 外國很悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />? <br />\n<br />\n說香港很多娛樂, 很多野玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想知有什麼好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n走在那些又多塵, 條路又迫, 又多自由行的油尖旺路上逛街嗎? <br />\n還是去戲院看戲, 去唱k? <br />\n還是去購物呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n外國很悶? <br />\n<br />\n完全想像不到香港有什麼好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所謂的娛樂不過是在屏風樓和馬路之間食塵 <br />\n擠迫在極之擁擠的環境裡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f109fb86563a01339cb384e8c2c2e13c34e431f","tid":2187392,"uid":224533,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:00:22.000Z","msg":"因為自己班friend喺香港啫"},{"pid":"672ae713745d8d226cc408a3d733b8ddb822757f","tid":2187392,"uid":24462,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:01:55.000Z","msg":"因為d人見識少<br />\n未見過世面以為香港係天堂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09a46737bbcf3821fa94d9bf671ede817e460f73","tid":2187392,"uid":8500,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:02:20.000Z","msg":"我都諗唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n星期六日你想搵個地方靜靜地拍拖都冇可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3248ea756afced64584a8719e39e8c1042d243b3","tid":2187392,"uid":273014,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:05:27.000Z","msg":"香港嘢食真係好多選擇，而且舖頭又開得晏，所以夜晚真係仲有好多嘢做，例如行街、睇戲、食飯、唱k。歐美的確唔少舖都早閂，去到夜晚，真係除咗飲酒、落club都冇咩好做。"},{"pid":"35cb28692c5d048cb7ecd13ededa38198fb2ebc9","tid":2187392,"uid":7708,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:10:19.000Z","msg":"想行街既話，d商鋪咁集中，好方便<br />\n想去郊外行山又近又多選擇，一條山徑有山又有海喺第度好難得<br />\n娛樂、文青cafe都大把啦，甚至其實行係舊區街道已經好多特色<br />\n其實係我地好少留意到香港有趣既一面"},{"pid":"1d274231214e2a619d71634afe4f3d7dffa21858","tid":2187392,"uid":133185,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:16:36.000Z","msg":"因為佢哋只係短暫過客。我哋去其他國家都一樣。"},{"pid":"a4d6c298957ae21b07d39eff51ce7b313354af50","tid":2187392,"uid":354503,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:43:53.000Z","msg":"你試過平日四五點啲舖頭關哂你就明<br />\n屌去蒲吧都要揸車出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49e64a91571d55e46022345406760c397c8d3bad","tid":2187392,"uid":208280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:50:33.000Z","msg":"啲鬼佬食唔少港女啦，點會悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f69a066191a3e67ccd201941f092836c0972264","tid":2187392,"uid":54930,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T16:08:10.000Z","msg":"因為景色再靚，冇人分享亦是無味<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d84417ccf86f6b09f448c1817090152e90cd6485","tid":2187392,"uid":363621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T16:19:36.000Z","msg":"隔離飯香<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}